        <div class="prose-dark mt-8">
          <p>Not every metric is measurable for every business. Voice answer selection testing, for example, requires a defined protocol: a set of test queries, a consistent testing environment, and a human reviewer recording outcomes. At small scale this is feasible. At enterprise scale it requires automation or specialist tooling. For most SMEs beginning their AEO programme, featured snippet win rate and PAA appearances — both measurable through Google Search Console and a basic SERP tracker — are sufficient starting metrics.</p>
        </div>
